66  QString value( "" );
67  if ( child == "general" ) { value = epanGeneral ->getSValue( type ); }
68  else if ( child == "rotor" ) { value = epanRotor ->getSValue( type ); }
69  else if ( child == "speeds" ) { value = epanSpeeds ->getSValue( type ); }
70  else if ( child == "cells" ) { value = epanCells ->getSValue( type ); }
71  else if ( child == "solutions") { value = epanSolutions->getSValue( type ); }
72  else if ( child == "optical" ) { value = epanOptical ->getSValue( type ); }
73  else if ( child == "ranges" ) { value = epanRanges ->getSValue( type ); }
74  else if ( child == "aprofile" ) { value = epanAProfile ->getSValue( type ); }
75  else if ( child == "submit" ) { value = epanUpload ->getSValue( type ); }

129 // Slot to handle a new panel selected
130 void US_ExperimentMain::newPanel( int panx )
131 {
132 DbgLv(1) << "newPanel panx=" << panx << "prev.panx=" << curr_panx << "usmode" << usmode;
133  // Save any changes in the old current panel
134  if ( curr_panx == panx ) return; // No change in panel
135 
136  if ( curr_panx == 0 ) epanGeneral ->savePanel();
137  else if ( curr_panx == 1 ) epanRotor ->savePanel();
138  else if ( curr_panx == 2 ) epanSpeeds ->savePanel();
139  else if ( curr_panx == 3 ) epanCells ->savePanel();
140  else if ( curr_panx == 4 ) epanSolutions->savePanel();
141  else if ( curr_panx == 5 ) epanOptical ->savePanel();
142  else if ( curr_panx == 6 ) epanRanges ->savePanel();
143  else if ( curr_panx == 7 )
144  {
145  if ( !usmode )
146  epanAProfile ->savePanel();
147  else
148  epanUpload ->savePanel();
149  }
150  else if ( curr_panx == 8 ) epanUpload ->savePanel();
151 
152  // Initialize the new current panel after possible changes
153  int pandiff = panx - curr_panx;
154  if ( panx == 0 ) epanGeneral ->initPanel();
155  else if ( panx == 1 ) epanRotor ->initPanel();
156  else if ( panx == 2 ) epanSpeeds ->initPanel();
157  else if ( panx == 3 ) epanCells ->initPanel();
158  else if ( panx == 4 ) // Solutions
159  {
160  if ( pandiff > 1 )
161  {
162  epanCells ->initPanel();
163  epanCells ->savePanel();
164  }
165  epanSolutions->initPanel();
166  }
167  else if ( panx == 5 ) // Optics
168  {
169  if ( pandiff > 1 )
170  {
171  epanCells ->initPanel();
172  epanCells ->savePanel();
173  epanSolutions->initPanel();
174  epanSolutions->savePanel();
175  }
176  epanOptical ->initPanel();
177  }
178  else if ( panx == 6 ) // Ranges
179  {
180  if ( pandiff > 1 )
181  {
182  epanCells ->initPanel();
183  epanCells ->savePanel();
184  epanSolutions->initPanel();
185  epanSolutions->savePanel();
186  epanOptical ->initPanel();
187  epanOptical ->savePanel();
188  }
189  epanRanges ->initPanel();
190  }
191  else if ( panx == 7 ) // AProfile OR Upload
192  {
193  if ( pandiff > 1 )
194  {
195  epanCells ->initPanel();
196  epanCells ->savePanel();
197  epanSolutions->initPanel();
198  epanSolutions->savePanel();
199  epanOptical ->initPanel();
200  epanOptical ->savePanel();
201  epanRanges ->initPanel();
202  epanRanges ->savePanel();
203  }
204  if ( !usmode ) // Active AProfile panel => 7 AProfile
205  epanAProfile ->initPanel();
206  else // No active AProfile panel => 7 Upload
207  epanUpload ->initPanel();
208  }
209  else if ( panx == 8 ) // Upload OR NONE
210  {
211  if ( pandiff > 1 )
212  {
213  epanCells ->initPanel();
214  epanCells ->savePanel();
215  epanSolutions->initPanel();
216  epanSolutions->savePanel();
217  epanOptical ->initPanel();
218  epanOptical ->savePanel();
219  epanRanges ->initPanel();
220  epanRanges ->savePanel();
221  epanAProfile ->initPanel();
222  epanAProfile ->savePanel();
223  }
224  epanUpload ->initPanel();
225  }
226 
227  curr_panx = panx; // Set new current panel
228 
229  // Update status flag for all panels
230  statUpdate();
231 }

4630 bool US_ExperGuiUpload::validExtinctionProfile( QString desc, QList< double > all_wvls,
4631  QList< double > ext_prof, QStringList& msg_to_user )
4632 {
4633  bool eprofile_ok;
4634  QString msg;
4635 
4636  //ranges from protocol
4637  int nwavl_p = all_wvls.count();
4638  double lo_wavl_p = all_wvls[ 0 ];
4639  double hi_wavl_p = all_wvls[ nwavl_p - 1 ];
4640 
4641  //ranges in extinction profile
4642  int nwavl_e = ext_prof.count();
4643  if ( nwavl_e > 0 )
4644  {
4645  double lo_wavl_e = ext_prof[ 0 ];
4646  double hi_wavl_e = ext_prof[ nwavl_e - 1 ];
4647 
4648  eprofile_ok = ( lo_wavl_e <= lo_wavl_p ) ? true : false;
4649  eprofile_ok = ( hi_wavl_e >= hi_wavl_p ) ? true : false;
4650 
4651  msg = "is out of range; ";
4652  }
4653  else //empty ext. profile
4654  {
4655  eprofile_ok = false;
4656  msg = "does not exist; ";
4657  }
4658 
4659  //check existence of all wavelengths (for non-empty ext.prof.)
4660  if ( nwavl_e > 0 )
4661  {
4662  QMap<double, bool> wvl_present;
4663  for (int i=0; i<all_wvls.size(); ++i)
4664  {
4665  double p_wvl = all_wvls[i];
4666  wvl_present[ p_wvl ] = false;
4667  for (int j=0; j<ext_prof.size(); j++)
4668  {
4669  double e_wvl = ext_prof[j];
4670  if ( p_wvl == e_wvl )
4671  {
4672  wvl_present[ p_wvl ] = true;
4673  break;
4674  }
4675  }
4676  }
4677  QMap < double, bool >::iterator ri;
4678  for ( ri = wvl_present.begin(); ri != wvl_present.end(); ++ri )
4679  {
4680  bool w_exists = ri.value();
4681  if ( !w_exists )
4682  {
4683  eprofile_ok = false;
4684  msg += "some wavelengths missing; ";
4685  break;
4686  }
4687  }
4688  }
4689 
4690  //messages
4691  if ( !eprofile_ok )
4692  msg_to_user << QString(tr("%1: Extinction profile %2"))
4693  .arg( desc )
4694  .arg( msg );
4695 
4696  return eprofile_ok;
4697 }
